stateDiagram-v2
    %% Server Search (US3) - State Diagram

    [*] --> HIDDEN : initial state

    HIDDEN --> VISIBLE_WITH_RESULTS : user types query, results found
    HIDDEN --> VISIBLE_NO_RESULTS : user types query, no matches

    VISIBLE_WITH_RESULTS --> VISIBLE_WITH_RESULTS : query changes, results found
    VISIBLE_WITH_RESULTS --> VISIBLE_NO_RESULTS : query changes, no matches
    VISIBLE_NO_RESULTS --> VISIBLE_WITH_RESULTS : query changes, results found
    VISIBLE_NO_RESULTS --> VISIBLE_NO_RESULTS : query changes, no matches

    VISIBLE_WITH_RESULTS --> HIDDEN : user selects server
    VISIBLE_WITH_RESULTS --> HIDDEN : user clears search
    VISIBLE_NO_RESULTS --> HIDDEN : user clears search

    note right of HIDDEN
        Search input empty
        No dropdown visible
    end note

    note right of VISIBLE_WITH_RESULTS
        GET /api/servers/search?q=...
        Dropdown shows matching servers
        with icons, names, member counts
    end note

    note right of VISIBLE_NO_RESULTS
        Query returned empty array
        Shows "No spaces found"
    end note
